OL,3,CMan injured in 'reckless' shooting
OL,5,FAn investigation is underway after a
OL,6,F19-year-old man was seriously injured
OL,7,Fin a "reckless" shooting.
OL,9,FPolice were called to Carlingford
OL,10,FClose, in Toxteth, Liverpool,
OL,11,Ffollowing reports that a man had
OL,12,Fsuffered an arm injury "consistent
OL,13,Fwith a firearm being used."
OL,15,FIt is believed the incident took place
OL,16,Fin the nearby Upper Parliament Street
OL,17,Farea just after 8:40pm on Wednesday, 3
OL,18,FJune.
