OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780585869
OL,3,CMan injured in 'reckless' shooting
OL,5,FThe teenager was taken to hospital for
OL,6,Ftreatment for injuries that are not
OL,7,Fbelieved to be life-threatening,
OL,8,FMerseyside Police said.
OL,10,FAn investigation is now underway, and
OL,11,Femergency services remain at the
OL,12,Fscene. Officers are currently carrying
OL,13,Fout house-to-house and CCTV enquiries
OL,14,Fin the local area.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Jay Boardman said:
OL,17,F"We are in the very early stages of
OL,18,Fthis investigation and we are seeking
OL,19,Fwitnesses and CCTV and Ring doorbell
OL,20,Ffootage to piece together what has
OL,21,Fhappened.
OL,26,@yD@AOU
