OL,3,CMan injured in 'reckless' shooting
OL,5,F"Firearms and the reckless people who
OL,6,Fchoose to carry and use them have no
OL,7,Fplace on the streets of Merseyside and
OL,8,Fwe would ask for the public's help to
OL,9,Flocate who is responsible and bring
OL,10,Fthem to justice."
